Where was the additional political agent?
The additional political agent was kidnapped ten days ago from South Waziristan by unidentified masked men.
Sources say that the agent was kidnapped by the Mulla Nazeer faction of local Taliban.
According to the local government, around 4 o'clock in the evening, Tuesday, the Additional Political Agent of South Waziristan, Aamir Latheef was brought to Wana Scouts camp, by a group of tribals.
However, they did not reveal who had kidnapped the additional political agent.
The locals however, are saying that the political agent was kidnapped by the Mulla Nazeer faction of local Taliban.
Aamir Latheef was kidnapped while he was going from Wana to Tank.
On the 11th of January in 2009, seven masked men kidnapped the additional political agent, Aamir Latheef, along with his driver, from the tribal area Karkandah of South Waziristan.
According to the government agent, the kidnappers first disarmed the guards and after that they seated the additional political agent in another car and took him away from there.
According to the local government, after the kidnapping of the additional political agent, security forces guarded all the check posts in South Waziristan and semi-tribal areas, and the people coming and going were searched thoroughly, and from the previous one week, the rulers have placed economic restrictions on Wana.
On December 8, 2008, an assistant political agent of north Wazirastan Asmatullah was kidnapped when he was going from Mir Ali to Bannu to enjoy his Eid vacation. A few days after this two people, including Tehsildar Amanullah, were killed by unknown masked perpetrators in north Wazirastan.
Victory of a British hacker in the court.
A 42-year-old British citizen has admitted that he hacked an American military website.
Gary has Asperger's syndrome. It should be kept in mind that an Asperger's patient has the obsession to do similar kinds of tasks.
His lawyers say that if he is handed over to America then he will commit suicide.
However, government officials say that they are no threat to Gary's health.
Lord justice Morskey and Mr. Justice Simon while announcing the decision said that Gary is permitted to file a review petition in a British court.

He added that the secretary of interior has noticed this issue.
But the government prosecutors say that the secretary of interior had used his authority.
Gary has never denied hacking the American military website.
In 2001 and 2002, Gary hacked an American computer system which caused a loss to the American government of eight hundred thousand dollars.
Gary hacked 97 computers including those of the American Navy and NASA.
However, Gary says that he did not do this with bad intentions, as he was just looking for information about aliens, which he thought the American government had kept secret.
Gary's mother, Janice Sharp, has said that she is happy with this decision.
Gary's lawyer has said that it is the right decision.
This case has continued since 2002, and finally a correct decision has been made.
